window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Brothers Blake and Mason have survived the 'system's' post-apocalyptic tutorial. They killed and cajoled their way into 'patronage' of a forest settlement, made useful (and beautiful) new allies, and for the moment things look good. A little too good.</p> <p>But for how long? The synthetic overlord who re-made the world has a plan. There's orcs and gnolls and all kinds of monstrous creatures looking for human blood. And whatever the system wants, whatever it's after, Mason knows there's only one way out: survival.</p> <p>But if he learns fast, improves enough, he just might get everything he ever wanted.</p> <p>With millions of views on Royal Road and Scribblehub, this series has more than 10 books worth of story, and more to come!</p> <p>The First Great Game is a litrpg/men's adventure sci-fi/fantasy series about two brothers who come of age and find incredible adventure, and equally incredible women, in a post-apocalyptic video game world.</p>"; 
